Name:		xorg-app-xedit
Version:	0.99.1
Release:	0.1
License:	MIT
Group:		X11/Applications
Source0:	http://xorg.freedesktop.org/releases/X11R7.0-RC1/app/xedit-%{version}.tar.bz2
